      <a class="indexterm" name="EpicMonsters(G-W)53"/>
      <p>A <a href="ch76s08.html#EpicMonsters(G-W)53">hoary steed's</a> natural weapons are treated as magic for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
          <div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="title"><a name="id2355534"/>Combat</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
          <div class="keyword">monsterinfo</div>
        </div>
        <a class="indexterm" name="EpicMonsters(G-W)54"/>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2355621"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="EpicMonsters(G-W)55"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Air Walk (Su):</strong></span> A <a href="ch76s08.html#EpicMonsters(G-W)53">hoary steed</a> can ride through the air as well as on the ground, as though affected by a permanent <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch43.html#SpellsA-B6">air walk</a></em></span> spell.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2355671"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="EpicMonsters(G-W)56"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Astral Projection and Etherealness (Su):</strong></span> These abilities function just like the spells of the same names as cast by a 20th-level caster.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2355768"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="EpicMonsters(G-W)57"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Magic Circle Against Good (Su):</strong></span> This ability continuously duplicates the effects of the spell. A <a href="ch76s08.html#EpicMonsters(G-W)53">hoary steed</a> cannot suppress this ability.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2355809"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="EpicMonsters(G-W)58"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Misty Breath (Su):</strong></span> The breath of a <a href="ch76s08.html#EpicMonsters(G-W)53">hoary steed</a> functions like a constant <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch48.html#SpellsM-O52">obscuring mist</a></em></span> spell.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2355858"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="EpicMonsters(G-W)59"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Immunities (Ex):</strong></span> A <a href="ch76s08.html#EpicMonsters(G-W)53">hoary steed</a> is immune to all <span class="emphasis"><em>charm</em></span> and <span class="emphasis"><em>hold</em></span> spells or abilities.</p>
          <p/>
        </div>
